<html
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
  xml:lang="en"
  lang="en"
  metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master"
  i18n:domain="launchpad">

<body>

<metal:leftportlets fill-slot="portlets_one">
  <div tal:replace="structure context/@@+portlet-latesttickets" />
</metal:leftportlets>

<metal:rightportlets fill-slot="portlets_two">
  <div tal:replace="structure context/@@+portlet-details" />
</metal:rightportlets>

<metal:main fill-slot="main">
  <metal:form use-macro="context/@@launchpad_form/form">

    <p metal:fill-slot="extra_info">
      Please enter a short description (at least 4 words) that describes your
      problem. We will use it to look for similar support requests that
      may already exist.
    </p>

    <div class="actions" metal:fill-slot="buttons">
      <input tal:replace="structure view/continue_action/render" />
    </div>

  </metal:form>
</metal:main>

<metal:help fill-slot="help">
  <p>For best results use a short but complete sentence that describes the
    problem. Be as specific as you can. Try to name the precise part of the
    application with which you're having a problem. Grammatical words like
    articles or prepositions, as well as other common words will be ignored.
  </p>
  <p>You can consult the
    <a href="https://help.launchpad.net/GettingSupportInLaunchpad">Getting
    Support in Launchpad</a> document for more information.</p>
</metal:help>
</body>
</html>

